{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/progress"]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/progress","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The pack’s current progress.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"title":"progress","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(py)progress","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"progress","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"property"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgress","text":"MLNOfflinePackProgress","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@MLNOfflinePackProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"progress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The progress of an inactive or completed pack is computed lazily, and all its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"fields are set to 0 by default. To request the pack’s progress, use the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-requestProgress"},{"type":"text","text":" method. To get notified when the progress becomes"},{"ty